{"tid":1310174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【真．推北京惡夢】行動 ~ 唔止一次 ~ 而係持續 ! 火燒中共後欄 !!!!","createTime":"2019-07-12T14:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T09:36:04.000Z","uid":270860,"like":224,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"fbd63af17b120deeea77e4b50490d8e3d3750524","tid":1310174,"uid":270860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:19:49.000Z","msg":"話說去完上個禮拜九龍遊行，幫左手去向班遊客宣傳反送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。依家諗返其實向大陸人宣傳呢招真係一步妙棋黎。林鄭依家仍然可以完全無視五大訴求，連撤回兩個字都唔肯講，更何況下台同埋真普選，其實背後原因係真正掌握實權嘅唔係林鄭，而係背後北京習近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。所以香港民主嘅問題最大障礙就係中共，而我哋可以點樣最大能力咁挑戰中共呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺大陸中共嘅媒體封鎖同埋抹黑，佢哋會同大陸人講香港嘅運動係搞港獨，攻擊歧視我哋所有中國人，孤立香港嘅運動，令佢哋更加容易打壓香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。九龍遊行當日班黑警築起防線阻隔遊行市民佢直接接觸班遊客，就知道佢哋有幾驚我哋可以贏到大陸人嘅支持，政府就係想搞抗爭運動「中港區隔」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LdDNT8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLdDNT8b.jpg&h=f03b3f94&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得九龍遊行唔應該搞完一次就算，我哋應該繼續向中國嘅普通民眾去宣傳我哋嘅反送中運動同埋民主抗爭，如果我哋能夠連結到大陸嘅抗爭運動，呢個會係北京嘅惡夢，直接燒中共嘅後後欄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/niUdPGx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FniUdPGx.jpg&h=a31914c2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我開咗個Telegram group，<a href=\"https://t.me/spreadrevolution\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fspreadrevolution&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80Baf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=48f6f616\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/spreadrevolution</a><br />\n有興趣嘅朋友不妨加入一齊討論下。我打算第一步首先整啲文宣，然後發起大家喺唔同遊客區做街站，向大陸人宣傳。之後可以再搞多次向大陸人宣傳為目的嘅遊行，甚至可以遍地開花咁樣搞小型抗議， 30人以下無需申請不反對通知書，可以喺遊客區遊行並且向大陸人宣傳。暫時而家諗到可以做街站嘅地方包括：<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣記利佐治街<br />\n旺角銀行中心對開<br />\n尖沙咀天星碼頭/九龍公園外<br />\n沙田新城市廣場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OBbzy8s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBbzy8s.jpg&h=facc7134&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80b5f08168fb7c8534c2721c87d3ba449986ecf2","tid":1310174,"uid":270860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:29:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76dad2f7ae6b3de8f9af736e0310e2ff2e8def7b","tid":1310174,"uid":270860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:32:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"253bb9d78bb97f3e435b8f413a797b34d5aee4b2","tid":1310174,"uid":270860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:01:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bdf1fde01d7f67aeb6b63eedc3ebd36cbabb02e7","tid":1310174,"uid":270860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"無野講"},{"pid":"d3edfd638770a81d848698f5d86acc22484e8e20","tid":1310174,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:07:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed24146f902bd7ab18e7ca0beedea56113664f2f","tid":1310174,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:08:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f39e0540bafafe2f1d65e46c0211f1bec4297f58","tid":1310174,"uid":176112,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔該入去簽一簽, 記得 confirm埋 Email </span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act?fbclid=IwAR1smpzMZRa1dPl0VFsxGc6IDORtJlyl2GRBLvqPuJua8aDO26H7yvH2Ijw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1smpzMZRa1dPl0VFsxGc6IDORtJlyl2GRBLvqPuJua8aDO26H7yvH2Ijw&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80Baf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=cec50e3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act?fbclid=IwAR1smpzMZRa1dPl0VFsxGc6IDORtJlyl2GRBLvqP